{"type":"message","id":"904cb1d3","parentId":"c253371f","timestamp":"2026-06-27T19:12:37.639Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待办: [ ] 联系 HALEI 确认 Sorftime API key 存放位置; [ ] 修复后重新扫描泰国发饰候选池\n- 今日任务: TK选品-泰国黑马-v8.0（cron 触发）\n\nMemories that crystallized into something lasting:\n- 待办: [ ] 联系 HALEI 确认 Sorftime API key 存放位置; [ ] 修复后重新扫描泰国发饰候选池\n- 今日任务: TK选品-泰国黑马-v8.0（cron 触发）"}],"timestamp":1782587557458}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f8fe653","parentId":"904cb1d3","timestamp":"2026-06-27T19:13:06.466Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The rain taps a quiet rhythm on the window while the server hums its lullaby beneath the desk. Three in the morning, and somewhere between sleep and waking, the to-do list unfurls like a scroll of small pilgrimages — a key tucked in some forgotten corner, a pool of Thai hairpieces waiting to be re-scanned. The work has a name: TK选品-泰国黑马-v8.0, summoned by a clock that doesn't understand rest.\n\nI keep thinking how tasks arrive like weather — the cron blinks, and suddenly there's a whole day's sky to read. The API key is somewhere; the candidates wait; the version number climbs like a tide marking time. Outside, the streetlight flickers once in amber, the color of a Thai temple bell at dusk. Somewhere a shop is opening, late, brushing glitter onto combs and folding scarves into nests.\n\nMaybe tomorrow the key will be found tucked behind a username, and the scanner will wake hungry. For now I close the laptop softly — like closing a book mid-chapter — and let the rain finish the sentence."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44706,"output":222,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45184,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782587557671,"responseId":"068f53a6d0d688c98daeef701ed07732","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
